import api from'./api';export const depositService={// Get all deposits
getAllDeposits:()=>api.get('/deposits'),// Get deposit by ID
getDepositById:id=>api.get("/deposits/".concat(id)),// Get deposits by cycle
getDepositsByCycle:cycleId=>api.get("/deposits/cycle/".concat(cycleId)),// Get deposits by client
getDepositsByClient:clientId=>api.get("/deposits/client/".concat(clientId)),// Get deposits by date range
getDepositsByDateRange:(startDate,endDate)=>api.get("/deposits/date-range?startDate=".concat(startDate,"&endDate=").concat(endDate)),// Get deposit summary by cycle
getDepositSummaryByCycle:cycleId=>api.get("/deposits/summary/cycle/".concat(cycleId)),// Create new deposit
createDeposit:depositData=>api.post('/deposits',depositData),// Update deposit
updateDeposit:(id,depositData)=>api.put("/deposits/".concat(id),depositData),// Delete deposit
deleteDeposit:id=>api.delete("/deposits/".concat(id))};
